{"title":"All-new Transition Spire 170mm 29er is the new enduro rig on the BC block","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/06/03/all-new-transition-spire-170mm-29er-is-the-new-enduro-rig-on-the-bc-block/","date":1622710815000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p><span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-box-3\"></span>Hot on the tail of the mixed wheel Transition Patrol is an all-new enduro bike; the Transition Spire. The bigger, burlier sibling comes in carbon and aluminium flavors, running 29″ wheels and 170mm travel, front and rear. Those figures place it firmly in the enduro race bike category but Transition say this is far from a one trick pony. Here’s more.</p><p><span><iframe width=\"696\" height=\"392\" data-ezsrc=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/H2a10RXxkds?version=3&amp;rel=1&amp;showsearch=0&amp;showinfo=1&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;fs=1&amp;hl=en-US&amp;autohide=2&amp;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation\" ezoid=\"0.21578027547546053\"></iframe></span></p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/02053851/transition-spire-170mm-travel-29er-enduro-bike-purple.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/02053851/transition-spire-170mm-travel-29er-enduro-bike-purple.jpg\" alt=\"transition spire purple enduro mountain bike 29&quot; wheels 170mm fork 170mm rear wheel travel\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/02053851/transition-spire-170mm-travel-29er-enduro-bike-purple.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/02053851/transition-spire-170mm-travel-29er-enduro-bike-purple-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2