and 30T Japanese Toray carbon fibres.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/02112237/transition-spire-29er-full-suspension-mountain-bike-alloy.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/02112237/transition-spire-29er-full-suspension-mountain-bike-alloy.jpg\" alt=\"transition spire alloy full suspension mtb huck\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/02112237/transition-spire-29er-full-suspension-mountain-bike-alloy.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/02112237/transition-spire-29er-full-suspension-mountain-bike-alloy-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/02112237/transition-spire-29er-full-suspension-mountain-bike-alloy-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/02112237/transition-spire-29er-full-suspension-mountain-bike-alloy-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/02112237/transition-spire-29er-full-suspension-mountain-bike-alloy-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/02112237/transition-spire-29er-full-suspension-mountain-bike-alloy-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/02112237/transition-spire-29er-full-suspension-mountain-bike-alloy-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/02112237/transition-spire-29er-full-suspension-mountain-bike-alloy-630x420.jpg 630w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb13 src ng ngcb13 srcset\