t spacing swingarm offers clearance for up to 2.6″ wide tires. For both the aluminium and carbon frames cable routing is guided internally for the dropper seat post and rear mech; the cable for the rear brake caliper is routed externally.&nbsp;<span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-leader-1\"></span></p><p>The Transition Spire gets a threaded bottom bracket and a press-in headset, with the headtube approved for use with a dual crown fork. Its 56mm/56mm dimensions can accommodate reach and angle adjust headsets for those who want to slacken off the head angle even further without also making the seat tube slacker.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/02111851/transition-spire-frame-details.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/02111851/transition-spire-frame-details.jpg\" alt=\"transition spire alloy\" width=\"1200\" height=\"744\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/02111851/transition-spire-frame-details.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/02111851/transition-spire-frame-details-297x184.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/02111851/transition-spire-frame-details-800x496.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/02111851/transition-spire-frame-details-120x74.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/02111851/transition-spire-frame-details-768x476.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/02111851/transition-spire-frame-details-696x432.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/02111851/transition-spire-frame-details-1068x662.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/02111851/transition-spire-frame-details-677x420.jpg 677w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/02111851/transition-spire-frame-details-356x220.jpg 356w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb13 src ng ngcb13 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/02111851/transition-spire-frame-details.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/02111851/transition-spire-frame-details.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/02111851/transition-spire-frame-details-297x184.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/02111851/transition-spire-frame-details-800x496.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/02111851/transition-spire-frame-details-120x74.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/02111851/transition-spire-frame-details-768x476.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/02111851/transition-spire-frame-details-696x432.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/02111851/transition-spire-frame-details-1068x662.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/02111851/transition-spire-frame-details-677x420.jpg 677w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/02111851/transition-spire-frame-details-356x220.jpg 356w\"></a></p><p>Inside the front triangle is an accessory mount and space for a water bottle. The frame is well protected with molded rubber panels on the driveside stays and the underside of the downtube.</p><h3>Pricing &amp; Availability</h3><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/02113055/transition-spire-carbon-and-alloy-model-colors.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/02113055/transition-spire-carbon-and-alloy-model-colors.jpg\" alt=\"transition spire colors\" width=\"1200\" height=\"744\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/02113055/transition-spire-carbon-and-alloy-model-colors.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/02113055/transition-spire-carbon-and-alloy-model-colors-297x184.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/02113055/transition-spire-carbon-and-alloy-model-colors-800x496.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/02113055/transition-spire-carbon-and-alloy-model-colors-120x74.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/02113055/transition-spire-carbon-and-alloy-model-colors-768x476.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/02113055/transition-spire-carbon-and-alloy-model-colors-696x432.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/02113055/transition-spire-carbon-and-alloy-model-colors-1068x662.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/02113055/transition-spire-carbon-and-alloy-model-colors-677x420.jpg 677w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-